📘 Overview

This repository contains my daily homework programming problems and solutions.
I upload the problems I practice every day to improve my coding skills, logical thinking, and problem-solving ability.

The goal of this repository is to maintain a consistent daily coding habit and track my progress over time.

📂 Repository Structure

Each file contains the solution for a homework problem.

Example structure:

Day01/

Day1_problem_1

Day1_problem_2

Day02/

Day2_problem_1

Day2_problem_2

